@startuml
title Resume Parser Service - Activity Diagram For Experience Header Analysis

start

:Receive header lines from current experience entry;
:Search for date range and remove it\nfrom header text;

if (Date range found?) then (yes)
  :Save original date range;
else (no)
  :Continue without date value;
endif

:Check company-like line;
:Check job title pattern;
:Check location pattern;
:Assign detected values to\ncompany, title and location;

if (Unknown text remains?) then (yes)
  :Move unknown fragments\nto remaining entry text;
else (no)
endif

:Return classified header fields;
stop
@enduml
